FBIS3-14138 "drnes056_n_94005" FBIS-NES-94-056 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Mar 1994 LEBANON Minister Denies Cover-Up in Bombing Probe NC2203183194 Beirut Voice of Lebanon in Arabic 1715 GMT 22 Mar 94 NC2203183194 Beirut Voice of Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Information Minister Michel Samahah met the president today and said that a cover-up of the investigation into recent bombings is impossible. He said that security and judicial authorities have seized the ring of people who are responsible for the bombings.
